#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/config/configRecording.qml:74
msgid "Schedules are managed in the widget itself: open the popup, press the music-note button in the footer to open My Music, then press the stopwatch button next to \"My Music\". Pick a station, start time, duration and repeat (once / daily / weekly) — the widget records in the background, even while nothing is playing."
msgstr "Ajastusi hallatakse vidinas endas: ava hüpikaken, vajuta jaluses noodinuppu, et avada „Minu muusika“, seejärel vajuta stopperinuppu „Minu muusika“ kõrval. Vali jaam, algusaeg, kestus ja kordus (üks kord / iga päev / iga nädal) — vidin salvestab taustal ka siis, kui midagi ei mängi."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/config/configRecording.qml:81
msgid "Recordings are saved to your music folder and are for personal use only — do not redistribute them."
