msgstr "Mängi seadmes (Chromecast, teler, kõlar)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2843
msgid "Play on"
msgstr "Mängi seadmes"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2856
msgid "This computer"
msgstr "See arvuti"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2872
msgid "System default output"
msgstr "Süsteemi vaikeväljund"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2899
msgid "All local outputs, in sync"
msgstr "Kõik kohalikud väljundid, sünkroonis"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2916
msgid "Plays on every connected speaker at the same time — wired outputs are delayed to stay in step with Bluetooth."
msgstr "Mängib korraga kõigis ühendatud kõlarites — juhtmega väljundeid viivitatakse, et need püsiksid Bluetoothiga samas taktis."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2930
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2937
msgid "Sync fine-tune"
msgstr "Süngi peenhäälestus"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2947
msgid "If the Bluetooth speaker still trails the wired ones, raise this until they play together."
msgstr "Kui Bluetooth-kõlar jääb juhtmega kõlaritest ikka maha, tõsta seda, kuni nad mängivad koos."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2965
msgid "Calibrate with the microphone"
msgstr "Kalibreeri mikrofoniga"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2970
msgid "Plays a few loud clicks through each speaker and measures with the microphone how far the Bluetooth speaker trails — the delay is set automatically."
msgstr "Mängib igast kõlarist paar valju klõpsu ja mõõdab mikrofoniga, kui palju Bluetooth-kõlar maha jääb — viide seatakse automaatselt."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2986
msgid "Listening to the clicks…"
msgstr "Kuulan klõpse…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3016
msgid "%1 plays in the group"
msgstr "%1 mängib grupis"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3029
msgid "Whether this speaker plays in the group — untick to leave it out without disconnecting it. Remembered for the device."
msgstr "Kas see kõlar mängib grupis — eemalda linnuke, et jätta ta mängust välja ilma ühendust katkestamata. Jäetakse seadmele meelde."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3042
msgid "Balance of %1"
msgstr "%1 balanss"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3051
msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device. It scales only what this widget plays; the per-device volume in the system's audio settings is a separate, untouched layer — which is why those numbers differ from these sliders."
msgstr "Selle kõlari osa helitugevusest — balanss järgib iga üldnivoo liigutust ja jäetakse seadme jaoks meelde. See mõjutab ainult selle vidina enda heli; süsteemi heliseadete seadmepõhine helitugevus on eraldi, puutumata kiht — seepärast erinevadki sealsed numbrid nendest liuguritest."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3068
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the left channel"
msgid "L"
msgstr "L"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3069
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the right channel"
msgid "R"
msgstr "R"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3070
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays a mono mix"
msgid "M"
msgstr "M"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3071
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays plain stereo"
msgid "ST"
msgstr "ST"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3076
msgid "Which channels this speaker plays: stereo, left only, right only, or a mono mix of both. Set one speaker to L and another to R for a true stereo pair — remembered for the device."
msgstr "Millised kanalid see kõlar mängib: stereo, ainult vasak, ainult parem või mõlema mono-miks. Pane üks kõlar L-i ja teine R-i peale — saad tõelise stereopaari; jäetakse seadmele meelde."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3106
msgid "Bluetooth"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3121
msgid "Bluetooth is off or no adapter is available — check System Settings."
msgstr "Bluetooth on välja lülitatud või adapterit pole — kontrolli süsteemiseadeid."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3132
msgid "No paired Bluetooth audio devices — pair the speaker once in System Settings and it appears here."
msgstr "Seotud Bluetooth-heliseadmeid pole — seo kõlar üks kord süsteemiseadetes ja see ilmub siia."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3146
msgid "%1 — connecting…"
msgstr "%1 — ühendumine…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3164
msgid "%1 — pairing…"
msgstr "%1 — seon…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3165
msgid "%1 — new, click to pair"
msgstr "%1 — uus, klõpsa sidumiseks"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3176
msgid "Pair a new speaker…"
msgstr "Seo uus kõlar…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3192
msgid "Searching — put the speaker in pairing mode…"
msgstr "Otsin — pane kõlar sidumisrežiimi…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3213
msgid "WiFi & network"
msgstr "WiFi ja võrk"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3245
msgid "%1 (speaker group)"
msgstr "%1 (kõlarigrupp)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3273
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Tasakaal"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3287
msgid "This device's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device."
msgstr "Selle seadme osa helitugevusest — tasakaal järgib iga põhiliuguri liigutust ja jäetakse seadme jaoks meelde."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3309
msgid "Each device buffers on its own, so rooms may play a few seconds apart. For perfectly synced speakers, group them in the Google Home app — the group appears here as a single device."
msgstr "Iga seade puhverdab voogu omaette, mistõttu ruumid võivad mängida mõne sekundi nihkega. Täpselt sünkroonis kõlarite jaoks loo Google Home'i äpis kõlarigrupp — grupp ilmub siia ühe seadmena."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3319
msgid "Stop casting everywhere"
msgstr "Peata esitus kõigis seadmetes"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3337
msgid "Searching for devices…"
msgstr "Otsin seadmeid…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3346
msgid "No devices found on your network"
